33.desc_0:
{Living Scroll}

This scroll contains the @spellName@ spell which is added into your spell book for as long as you carry the scroll.

When attacking monsters with no hero, there is a 20% chance (times the number of Living Scrolls equipped), that each round a Living Spell Scroll will cast its spell on a random target.

